com.bigdata.service.geospatial

Class ZOrderIndexBigMinAdvancer

  • java.lang.Object
    • cutthecrap.utils.striterators.FilterBase
      • com.bigdata.btree.filter.Advancer<SPO>
        • com.bigdata.service.geospatial.ZOrderIndexBigMinAdvancer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ITupleFilter<SPO>, IFilter, IPropertySet, Serializable, Cloneable

    public class ZOrderIndexBigMinAdvancer
extends Advancer<SPO>
    Advances the cursor to the next zOrderKey that is greater or equal than the first point in the next region. Note that this next key is not necessarily a hit (but, depending on the data) this might be a miss again.
    Author:
    Bryan Thompson
